CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 21, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "Fire, Not a Bomb - This rear view of the three Jewel Street homes shows the remains left by the six-alarm fire which consumed the frame structure early last Friday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Three wood frame houses with severe fire and water damage after six-alarm fire, Jewel Street, Polish Hill
